{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"33911fcf80","title":"对张闻天来信的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"dd59cf69b2","index":0,"year":1959,"month":8,"day":18,"articleId":"33911fcf80"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"b0e4f99ee9","name":"张闻天","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji42","name":"毛泽东全集第42卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/42-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji42":{"comments":[{"id":"089f8ab53b","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"33911fcf80","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"张闻天，又名洛甫。"},{"id":"1ec0b003bd","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"33911fcf80","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"张闻天1959年8月18日上午给毛泽东的信说：“我这次动了大手术，对我以后的身体健康，定会起良好的影响。我夷心地感谢你和中央其他同志所给予我的帮助。我一定要同昨天的那个反动的我，永远决绝。今天读到你关于枚乘《七发》的批语和机关枪及其他，更使我深为感动。”“因为没有得到你的通知，所以我没有去见你。我今天下山，希望能在北京，再见到你，并希望你多多指导。”毛泽东在批示印发这封信时，拟题为：“洛南同志8月18日上午庐山临别赠言，给毛泽东。"}],"contents":[{"id":"bb55e1c1ea","type":"title","text":"对张闻天\"来信的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"33911fcf80"},{"id":"089f8ab53b","type":"paragraph","text":"印发各同志。印160多份，发给每人一份。走了的，航送或邮送去。我以极大的热情欢迎洛甫这封信","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"33911fcf80"},{"id":"1ec0b003bd","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"33911fcf80"},{"id":"999ac1483e","type":"paragraph","text":"八月十八日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"33911fcf80"}],"page":{"id":"b7ae8a976d","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"33911fcf80","start":306,"end":306}}}},"__N_SSG":true}